title: What's In The Background (feat. Brian Six & Kilah Fox)
description:
Show Philadelphia favorite's Brian Six & Kilah Fox join the show! The gang watches subway fight and try to figure out exactly what part is fake. The crew admit to the songs they have playing in the background to set the mood.
